      "content": "it's not just \"distorted perception\" though. it's everywhere. i see it on my phone, i hear it in the halls... it's like there's no way to win. like no matter how much i try to ignore them or be better, they're just gonna keep finding new ways to tear me down. it feels like i'm stuck in a room where the walls are just closing in and there's no door. i just feel so incredibly alone in this.",
